import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

theorem omni_math_problem_0 (n : ℕ) (hn : 0 < n) :
    IsLeast {∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (σ i).val (2 * i.val - 1) | (σ : Equiv.Perm (Finset.Icc 1 n))} (∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (n + 1 - i) (2 * i - 1)) := by

  have h_mem :
      (∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (n + 1 - i) (2 * i - 1)) ∈
        {∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (σ i).val (2 * i.val - 1) |
            (σ : Equiv.Perm (Finset.Icc 1 n))} := by
    refine' ⟨Equiv.refl (Finset.Icc 1 n), ?_⟩

    simp

  refine' ⟨h_mem, ?_⟩
  intro σ hσ

  have h_eq :
      (∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (n + 1 - i) (2 * i - 1)) =
        ∑ i : Finset.Icc 1 n, min (σ i).val (2 * i.val - 1) := by
    simpa [Equiv.toFun_eq] using rfl

  simpa [h_eq] using hσ

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  sum_A_le_lambda
  (x : ℕ → ℝ) (hx : ∀ i, 1 ≤ i ∧ i ≤ 2002 → x i ≥ 0) :
  sum_A_k_terms x ≤ lambda_ans * a_sequence 2002 :=
by
  have h_nonneg : (0 : ℝ) ≤ sum_A_k_terms x := by
    apply Finset.sum_nonneg
    intro k hk
    by_cases h1 : (1 : ℕ) ≤ k
    · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1] <;>
        (try positivity) <;>
        (try
          {
            apply div_nonneg
            · 
              simp_all [Finset.mem_range] <;> norm_num <;> linarith [hx k ⟨h1, by
                have : k ≤ 2002 := by
                  simp [Finset.mem_range] at hk
                  omega
                exact this⟩]
            · 
              have hden : (0 : ℝ) ≤ ( ∑ i in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
                  if k ≤ i then x i else 0 + (↑(k * Nat.pred k) : ℝ) / 2 + 1) ^ 2 := by
                positivity
              positivity
          })
    · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1]
  have h_a_pos : (0 : ℝ) < a_sequence 2002 := by
    have h1 : a_sequence 2002 = (1 / 4 : ℝ) * (1 + a_sequence 2001) ^ 2 := by
      rfl
    positivity
  have h_lambda_pos : (0 : ℝ) < lambda_ans * a_sequence 2002 := by
    positivity

  have : sum_A_k_terms x ≤ (1 / 2005004 : ℝ) * a_sequence 2002 := by
    norm_num [lambda_ans] at *
    <;>
    (try
      nlinarith [h_nonneg, h_a_pos, h_lambda_pos])
    <;>
    (try
      linarith)
  simpa [lambda_ans] using this

lemma lambda_minimal (a : ℝ)
  (ha :
    ∀ (x : ℕ → ℝ),
      (∀ i, 1 ≤ i ∧ i ≤ 2002 → x i ≥ 0) →
      sum_A_k_terms x ≤ a * a_sequence 2002) :
  lambda_ans ≤ a :=
by
  by_contra hlt
  have hlt' : a < lambda_ans := by linarith
  have h_a_pos : (0 : ℝ) < a_sequence 2002 := by
    have h1 : a_sequence 2002 = (1 / 4 : ℝ) * (1 + a_sequence 2001) ^ 2 := by
      rfl
    positivity
  have h_ex :
      ∃ (x : ℕ → ℝ),
        (∀ i, 1 ≤ i ∧ i ≤ 2002 → x i ≥ 0) ∧
        sum_A_k_terms x > a * a_sequence 2002 := by
    refine ⟨fun _ => (2003 : ℝ), ?_, ?_⟩
    · intro i hi
      norm_num at hi ⊢ <;>
        (try omega) <;>
        (try norm_num) <;>
        (try linarith)
    · 
      have h_sum_eq :
          sum_A_k_terms (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) =
            (∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
                if 1 ≤ k then A_k_term (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) k else 0) := by
        rfl
      have h_pos_term :
          (0 : ℝ) ≤
            ∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
              if 1 ≤ k then A_k_term (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) k else 0 := by
        apply Finset.sum_nonneg
        intro k hk
        by_cases h1 : (1 : ℕ) ≤ k
        · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1] <;> norm_num
          all_goals try positivity
        · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1]
      have h_gt :
          (∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
              if 1 ≤ k then A_k_term (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) k else 0) >
            a * a_sequence 2002 := by
        have h_sum_le :
            (∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
                if 1 ≤ k then A_k_term (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) k else 0) ≤
              2002 * (2003 : ℝ) := by
          calc
            (∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1),
                if 1 ≤ k then A_k_term (fun _ => (2003 : ℝ)) k else 0)
                ≤ ∑ k in Finset.range (2002 + 1), (2003 : ℝ) := by
                  apply Finset.sum_le_sum
                  intro k hk
                  by_cases h1 : (1 : ℕ) ≤ k
                  · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1] <;> norm_num <;>
                      (try
                        {
                          apply (div_le_iff (by positivity)).mpr
                          <;>
                          (try norm_num) <;>
                          (try nlinarith)
                        })
                  · simp [A_k_term, N_val, h1] <;> norm_num
                _ = (2002 + 1) * (2003 : ℝ) := by
                  simp [Finset.sum_const, Finset.card_range] <;> ring_nf
                _ ≤ 2002 * (2003 : ℝ) := by norm_num
        have h_a_mul_lt :
            a * a_sequence 2002 < (1 / 2005004 : ℝ) * a_sequence 2002 := by
          nlinarith
        have h_lambda_mul :
            (1 / 2005004 : ℝ) * a_sequence 2002 ≤ 2002 * (2003 : ℝ) := by
          have h_a_le_one : a_sequence 2002 ≤ (1 : ℝ) := by
            have hRec :
                a_sequence 2002 = (1 / 4 : ℝ) * (1 + a_sequence 2001) ^ 2 := by
              rfl
            have hInd : ∀ n ≤ 2002, a_sequence n ≤ (1 : ℝ) := by
              intro n hn
              induction' hn with n hn ih
              · norm_num [a_sequence]
              · cases n with
                | zero => norm_num [a_sequence]
                | succ n =>
                  simp_all [a_sequence, Nat.succ_eq_add_one] <;>
                    (try norm_num at * <;> nlinarith)
            exact hInd 2002 (by norm_num)
          nlinarith
        linarith
      simpa [h_sum_eq] using h_gt
  obtain ⟨x, hx_nonneg, hx_sum⟩ := h_ex
  have h_bound : sum_A_k_terms x ≤ a * a_sequence 2002 := ha x hx_nonneg
  linarith

theorem omni_math_problem_1 :
  (∀ (x : ℕ → ℝ),
    (∀ i, 1 ≤ i ∧ i ≤ N_val → x i ≥ 0) →
    sum_A_k_terms x ≤ lambda_ans * (a_sequence N_val)) ∧
  (∀ (a : ℝ),
    (∀ (x : ℕ → ℝ),
      (∀ i, 1 ≤ i ∧ i ≤ N_val → x i ≥ 0) →
      sum_A_k_terms x ≤ a * (a_sequence N_val)) →
    lambda_ans ≤ a) :=
by
  constructor
  · intro x hx

    have h₁ :
        sum_A_k_terms x ≤ lambda_ans * a_sequence 2002 :=
      sum_A_le_lambda (x := x) (hx := hx)
    simpa [N_val] using h₁
  · intro a ha
    have h₂ :
        lambda_ans ≤ a :=
      lambda_minimal (a := a) (ha := ha)
    simpa [N_val] using h₂

import Aesop

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  denom1_ne_zero (x y z : ℝ)
    (h₀ : (x + y) / (1 + z) = (1 - z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2))
    (h₁ : 1 + z ≠ 0) :
    x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2 ≠ 0 := by
  by_contra h
  have hxy : x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2 = 0 := by simpa using h
  have hpos : x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2 > 0 := by
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - y), sq_nonneg y]
  linarith

lemma denom2_ne_zero (x y z : ℝ)
    (h₁ : (x - y) / (3 - z) = (9 + 3 * z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2))
    (h₂ : 3 - z ≠ 0) :
    x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2 ≠ 0 := by
  by_contra h
  have hxy : x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2 = 0 := by simpa using h
  have hpos : x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2 > 0 := by
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x + y), sq_nonneg y]
  linarith

theorem omni_math_problem_4 (x y z : ℝ) (h₀ : (x + y) / (1 + z) = (1 - z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2)) (h₁ : (x - y) / (3 - z) = (9 + 3 * z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2)) :
    x = (14 ^ (1 / 3 : ℝ)) := by

  have h₂ : 1 + z ≠ 0 := by
    by_contra h
    have hzero : 1 + z = 0 := by simpa using h
    have h₀' : (x + y) / (1 + z) = (1 - z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2) := h₀
    rw [hzero] at h₀'
    norm_num at h₀' ⊢
    <;>
    (try simp_all [div_eq_mul_inv]) <;>
    (try
      {
        have hpos : (1 - z + z ^ 2 : ℝ) > 0 := by
          nlinarith [sq_nonneg (z - 1)]
        have hden : x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2 ≠ 0 := by
          by_contra hden
          have : x ^ 2 - x * y + y ^ 2 = 0 := by simpa using hden
          nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - y), sq_nonneg y]
        field_simp [hden] at h₀'
        nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x + y), sq_nonneg (x - y),
          sq_nonneg (z + 1), sq_nonneg (z - 1)]
      })
  have h₃ : 3 - z ≠ 0 := by
    by_contra h
    have hzero : 3 - z = 0 := by simpa using h
    have h₁' : (x - y) / (3 - z) = (9 + 3 * z + z ^ 2) / (x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2) := h₁
    rw [hzero] at h₁'
    norm_num at h₁' ⊢
    <;>
    (try simp_all [div_eq_mul_inv]) <;>
    (try
      {
        have hpos : (9 + 3 * z + z ^ 2 : ℝ) > 0 := by
          nlinarith [sq_nonneg (z + 3)]
        have hden : x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2 ≠ 0 := by
          by_contra hden
          have : x ^ 2 + x * y + y ^ 2 = 0 := by simpa using hden
          nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x + y), sq_nonneg y]
        field_simp [hden] at h₁'
        nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - y), sq_nonneg (x + y),

name: omni_math_problem_18
code:
import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  sqrt_diff_eq (x : ℝ) (hx : 2 ≤ x)
    (h :
      1 / (Real.sqrt x + Real.sqrt (x - 2)) +
        1 / (Real.sqrt (x + 2) + Real.sqrt x) = 1 / 4) :
    Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2) = 1 / 2 := by
  have h₃ : 0 ≤ x := by linarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ x - 2 := by linarith
  have h₅ : 0 ≤ x + 2 := by linarith
  have h₆ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt x := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₇ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x - 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₈ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x + 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₉ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt x * Real.sqrt (x - 2) := by positivity
  have h₁₀ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x + 2) * Real.sqrt x := by positivity
  have h₁₁ :
      1 / (Real.sqrt x + Real.sqrt (x - 2)) =
        (Real.sqrt x - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) / 2 := by
    have h₁₂ : Real.sqrt x + Real.sqrt (x - 2) ≠ 0 := by
      nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg x, Real.sqrt_nonneg (x - 2),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x - 2 by linarith)]
    have h₁₃ :
        (Real.sqrt x + Real.sqrt (x - 2)) *
          (Real.sqrt x - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) = 2 := by
      nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x - 2 by linarith),
        Real.sqrt_nonneg x, Real.sqrt_nonneg (x - 2)]
    field_simp [h₁₂]
    <;> nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x - 2 by linarith),
      Real.sqrt_nonneg x, Real.sqrt_nonneg (x - 2)]
  have h₁₂ :
      1 / (Real.sqrt (x + 2) + Real.sqrt x) =
        (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt x) / 2 := by
    have h₁₃ : Real.sqrt (x + 2) + Real.sqrt x ≠ 0 := by
      nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg (x + 2), Real.sqrt_nonneg x,
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x + 2 by linarith),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith)]
    have h₁₄ :
        (Real.sqrt (x + 2) + Real.sqrt x) *
          (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt x) = 2 := by
      nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x + 2 by linarith),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith),
        Real.sqrt_nonneg (x + 2), Real.sqrt_nonneg x]
    field_simp [h₁₃]
    <;> nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x + 2 by linarith),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x by linarith),
      Real.sqrt_nonneg (x + 2), Real.sqrt_nonneg x]
  rw [h₁₁, h₁₂] at h
  ring_nf at h ⊢
  nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg (x + 2), Real.sqrt_nonneg (x - 2),
    Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x + 2 by linarith),
    Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x - 2 by linarith)]

lemma linear_eq (x : ℝ) (hx : 2 ≤ x)
    (h₁ : Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2) = 1 / 2) :
    2 * x - 2 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 1 / 4 := by
  have h₂ : 0 ≤ x := by linarith
  have h₃ : 0 ≤ x - 2 := by linarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ x + 2 := by linarith
  have h₅ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x + 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₆ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x - 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₇ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x + 2) * Real.sqrt (x - 2) := by positivity

  have h₈ : (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2 = (1 / 2) ^ 2 := by
    rw [h₁]

  have h₉ :
      (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2 =
        2 * x - 2 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) := by

    have h₁₀ :
        (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2 =
          (x + 2) + (x - 2) - 2 * Real.sqrt ((x + 2) * (x - 2)) := by

      have h₁₀₁ : 0 ≤ (x + 2) := by linarith
      have h₁₀₂ : 0 ≤ (x - 2) := by linarith
      have h₁₀₃ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x + 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
      have h₁₀₄ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x - 2) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
      calc
        (Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2
            = (Real.sqrt (x + 2)) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2
                - 2 * (Real.sqrt (x + 2) * Real.sqrt (x - 2)) := by
              ring
        _ = (x + 2) + (x - 2) - 2 * (Real.sqrt (x + 2) * Real.sqrt (x - 2)) := by
              have h₁₀₅ : (Real.sqrt (x + 2)) ^ 2 = x + 2 := by
                rw [Real.sq_sqrt] <;> linarith
              have h₁₀₆ : (Real.sqrt (x - 2)) ^ 2 = x - 2 := by
                rw [Real.sq_sqrt] <;> linarith
              rw [h₁₀₅, h₁₀₆]
        _ = (x + 2) + (x - 2) - 2 * Real.sqrt ((x + 2) * (x - 2)) := by
              have h₁₀₇ : Real.sqrt (x + 2) * Real.sqrt (x - 2) =
                  Real.sqrt ((x + 2) * (x - 2)) := by
                rw [Real.sqrt_mul] <;> nlinarith
              rw [h₁₀₇]
              <;> ring
    have h₁₁ : Real.sqrt ((x + 2) * (x - 2)) = Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) := by
      have h₁₂ : (x + 2) * (x - 2) = x ^ 2 - 4 := by ring
      rw [h₁₂]
    rw [h₁₀, h₁₁]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg (x ^ 2 - 4),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x ^ 2 - 4 by nlinarith)]

  have h₁₀ : (1 / 2 : ℝ) ^ 2 = 1 / 4 := by norm_num
  nlinarith [h₈, h₉, h₁₀]

lemma isolate_sqrt (x : ℝ) (hx : 2 ≤ x)
    (h₂ : 2 * x - 2 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 1 / 4) :
    8 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 8 * x - 1 := by
  have h₃ : 0 ≤ x := by linarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ x - 2 := by linarith
  have h₅ : 0 ≤ x ^ 2 - 4 := by nlinarith
  have h₆ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₇ : (Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4)) ^ 2 = x ^ 2 - 4 := by
    rw [Real.sq_sqrt] <;> nlinarith
  nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x ^ 2 - 4 by nlinarith),
    Real.sqrt_nonneg (x ^ 2 - 4)]

lemma final_linear (x : ℝ) (hx : 2 ≤ x)
    (h₃ : 8 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 8 * x - 1) :
    x = 257 / 16 := by
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ x := by linarith
  have h₅ : 0 ≤ x - 2 := by linarith
  have h₆ : 0 ≤ x ^ 2 - 4 := by nlinarith
  have h₇ : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) := Real.sqrt_nonneg _
  have h₈ : (Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4)) ^ 2 = x ^ 2 - 4 := by
    rw [Real.sq_sqrt] <;> nlinarith
  have h₉ : (8 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4)) ^ 2 = (8 * x - 1) ^ 2 := by
    rw [h₃]
  have h₁₀ : 64 * (x ^ 2 - 4) = (8 * x - 1) ^ 2 := by
    nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ x ^ 2 - 4 by nlinarith)]
  nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - 257 / 16)]

theorem omni_math_problem_18 (x : ℝ) (hx : 2 ≤ x) (h : 1 / (sqrt x + sqrt (x - 2)) + 1 / (sqrt (x + 2) + sqrt x) = 1 / 4) :
    x = 257 / 16 := by
  have h₁ : Real.sqrt (x + 2) - Real.sqrt (x - 2) = 1 / 2 :=
    sqrt_diff_eq (x := x) hx h
  have h₂ : 2 * x - 2 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 1 / 4 :=
    linear_eq (x := x) hx h₁
  have h₃ : 8 * Real.sqrt (x ^ 2 - 4) = 8 * x - 1 :=
    isolate_sqrt (x := x) hx h₂
  have h₄ : x = 257 / 16 :=
    final_linear (x := x) hx h₃
  exact h₄

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  h₁' (A B C D : ℝ) (h₀ : A < B ∧ B < C ∧ C < D)
    (h₁ : (B - A) / (C - A) = 1 / 5) :
    B - A = (1 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := by
  have h₅ : C - A > 0 := by linarith
  have h₆ : (B - A) / (C - A) = 1 / 5 := by linarith
  have h₇ : B - A = (1 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := by
    have h₈ : (C - A) ≠ 0 := by linarith
    field_simp at h₆ ⊢
    nlinarith
  exact h₇

lemma h₂' (A B C D : ℝ) (h₀ : A < B ∧ B < C ∧ C < D)
    (h₂ : (C - B) / (D - C) = 2 / 1) :
    C - B = 2 * (D - C) := by
  have h₅ : D - C > 0 := by linarith
  have h₆ : (C - B) / (D - C) = 2 / 1 := by linarith
  have h₇ : C - B = 2 * (D - C) := by
    have h₈ : (D - C) ≠ 0 := by linarith
    field_simp at h₆ ⊢
    nlinarith
  exact h₇

lemma h₃ (A B C D : ℝ) (h₀ : A < B ∧ B < C ∧ C < D)
    (h₁ : (B - A) / (C - A) = 1 / 5)
    (h₂ : (C - B) / (D - C) = 2 / 1) :
    D - C = (2 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := by
  have h₃ : B - A = (1 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := h₁' A B C D h₀ h₁
  have h₄ : C - B = 2 * (D - C) := h₂' A B C D h₀ h₂
  have h₅ : C - B = (4 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := by
    have h₅₁ : C - B = (C - A) - (B - A) := by ring
    rw [h₅₁, h₃]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> norm_num
    <;> linarith
  have h₆ : (4 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) = 2 * (D - C) := by linarith
  have h₇ : D - C = (2 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := by
    linarith
  exact h₇

lemma h₄ (A B C D : ℝ) (h₀ : A < B ∧ B < C ∧ C < D)
    (h₁ : (B - A) / (C - A) = 1 / 5)
    (h₂ : (C - B) / (D - C) = 2 / 1) :
    D - C = 2 * (B - A) := by
  have h₃' : D - C = (2 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := h₃ A B C D h₀ h₁ h₂
  have h₁' : B - A = (1 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := h₁' A B C D h₀ h₁
  have h₅ : C - A = 5 * (B - A) := by
    have h₅₁ : B - A = (1 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := h₁'
    linarith
  have h₆ : D - C = 2 * (B - A) := by
    rw [h₃', h₅]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> norm_num
    <;> linarith
  exact h₆

theorem omni_math_problem_19
  (A B C D : ℝ)
  (h₀ : A < B ∧ B < C ∧ C < D)
  (h₁ : (B - A) / (C - A) = 1 / 5)
  (h₂ : (C - B) / (D - C) = 2 / 1)
  : (B - A) / (D - C) = 1 / 2 := by
  have h₃' : D - C = (2 / 5 : ℝ) * (C - A) := h₃ A B C D h₀ h₁ h₂
  have h₄' : D - C = 2 * (B - A) := h₄ A B C D h₀ h₁ h₂
  have h₅ : D - C > 0 := by linarith
  have h₆ : (B - A) / (D - C) = 1 / 2 := by
    have h₇ : D - C = 2 * (B - A) := h₄'
    have h₈ : (B - A) / (D - C) = (B - A) / (2 * (B - A)) := by
      rw [h₇]
      <;> ring_nf
    rw [h₈]
    have h₉ : B - A > 0 := by linarith
    have h₁₀ : (B - A) ≠ 0 := by linarith
    field_simp [h₁₀]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> field_simp [h₁₀]
    <;> linarith
  exact h₆

import Aesop

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  rational_eq_iff_mul_eq {x y : ℕ} (hx : x > 0) (hy : y > 0) :
    ((x : ℚ) / 4 = 9 / y) ↔ x * y = 36 := by
  constructor
  · intro h
    have h' : (x : ℚ) * y = 36 := by
      field_simp [Nat.cast_ne_zero.mpr (Nat.ne_of_gt hx),
                  Nat.cast_ne_zero.mpr (Nat.ne_of_gt hy)] at h
      norm_cast at h ⊢
      <;> ring_nf at h ⊢ <;> norm_num at h ⊢ <;> nlinarith
    have : x * y = 36 := by
      norm_cast at h' ⊢
      <;> ring_nf at h' ⊢ <;> norm_num at h' ⊢ <;> nlinarith
    exact this
  · intro h
    have h' : (x : ℚ) * y = 36 := by
      norm_cast
      <;> simp [h] <;> norm_num
    have hy_ne : (y : ℚ) ≠ 0 := by
      have : (y : ℚ) ≠ 0 := by
        exact_mod_cast (Nat.ne_of_gt hy)
      exact this
    field_simp [hy_ne] at h' ⊢
    <;> norm_cast at h' ⊢ <;> simp_all [mul_comm] <;> nlinarith

theorem omni_math_problem_20 :
  {(x, y) : ℕ × ℕ | x > 0 ∧ y > 0 ∧ (x : ℚ) / 4 = 9 / y}.ncard = 9 := by

  have set_eq :
      {(x, y) : ℕ × ℕ | x > 0 ∧ y > 0 ∧ (x : ℚ) / 4 = 9 / y} =
        {(x, y) : ℕ × ℕ | x > 0 ∧ y > 0 ∧ x * y = 36} := by
    apply Set.ext
    intro p
    rcases p with ⟨x, y⟩
    simp only [Set.mem_setOf_eq]
    constructor
    · intro h
      rcases h with ⟨hx, hy, hxy⟩
      have hmul : x * y = 36 := (rational_eq_iff_mul_eq hx hy).1 hxy
      exact ⟨hx, hy, hmul⟩
    · intro h
      rcases h with ⟨hx, hy, hmul⟩
      have hxy : (x : ℚ) / 4 = 9 / y := by
        have : x * y = 36 := hmul
        have h' : (x : ℚ) * y = 36 := by
          norm_cast
          <;> simp [this] <;> norm_num
        have hy_ne : (y : ℚ) ≠ 0 := by
          have : (y : ℚ) ≠ 0 := by
            exact_mod_cast (Nat.ne_of_gt hy)
          exact this
        field_simp [hy_ne] at h' ⊢
        <;> norm_cast at h' ⊢ <;> simp_all [mul_comm] <;> nlinarith
      exact ⟨hx, hy, hxy⟩

  have ncard_eq_nine :
      {(x, y) : ℕ × ℕ | x > 0 ∧ y > 0 ∧ x * y = 36}.ncard = 9 := by
    have hfinset :
        (({(x, y) : ℕ × ℕ | x > 0 ∧ y > 0 ∧ x * y = 36} : Set (ℕ × ℕ)).toFinset).card = 9 := by
      norm_num [Set.toFinset_eq] <;> decide
    simpa [Set.ncard_eq_toFinset_card] using hfinset

  simpa [set_eq] using ncard_eq_nine

lemma  P_ne_zero {P : MvPolynomial (Fin 2) ℝ}

          (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0) *
            (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0 - MvPolynomial.C 1)) :
    P ≠ 0 := by
  have hcoeff : (P.coeff (MvPolynomial.C (1 : ℝ) * MvPolynomial.X 1)) ≠ (0 : ℝ) := by

    simp [hP, MvPolynomial.coeff_mul, MvPolynomial.coeff_C_mul,
          MvPolynomial.coeff_X_pow, Nat.cast_ofNat] <;> norm_num
  intro hzero
  have : (P.coeff (MvPolynomial.C (1 : ℝ) * MvPolynomial.X 1)) = 0 := by
    simpa [hzero] using (by rfl :
      (0 : MvPolynomial (Fin 2) ℝ).coeff (MvPolynomial.C (1 : ℝ) * MvPolynomial.X 1) = 0)
  exact hcoeff this

lemma eval_at_int_parts_eq_zero {P : MvPolynomial (Fin 2) ℝ}
    (hP :
        P =
          (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0) *
            (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0 - MvPolynomial.C 1)) :
    ∀ a : ℝ,
      MvPolynomial.eval (fun n : Fin 2 => if n = 0 then (⌊a⌋ : ℝ) else (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℝ)) P = 0 := by
  intro a

  have hP' : P =
        (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0) *
          (MvPolynomial.X 1 - MvPolynomial.C 2 * MvPolynomial.X 0 - MvPolynomial.C 1) := hP
  rw [hP']

  have hfloor : (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) = 2 * ⌊a⌋ ∨ (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) = 2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 := by

    have h₁ : (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) = 2 * ⌊a⌋ ∨ (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) = 2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 := by
      have hle : (2 * ⌊a⌋ : ℤ) ≤ ⌊2 * a⌋ := by
        have : (2 * ⌊a⌋ : ℤ) ≤ ⌊2 * a⌋ := by
          apply Int.le_floor.mpr
          have : (2 * ⌊a⌋ : ℝ) ≤ 2 * a := by
            have : (⌊a⌋ : ℝ) ≤ a := Int.floor_le a
            linarith
          exact_mod_cast this
        exact this
      have hge : (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) ≤ 2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 := by
        apply Int.le_of_lt_add_one
        have hlt : (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) < 2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 := by
          have : (⌊2 * a⌋ : ℤ) < 2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 := by
            apply Int.floor_lt.mpr
            have : (2 * a : ℝ) < (2 * ⌊a⌋ + 1 : ℝ) := by
              have h₁ : (a : ℝ) < (⌊a⌋ + 1 : ℝ) := Int.lt_floor_add_one a
              linarith
            exact_mod_cast this
          exact this
        exact this
      omega

            simpa [Finset.sum_sdiff hsub] using rfl

        have hle' : P.degree ≤ 1 := by

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  is_eventually_periodic (q : ℕ → ℚ) : Prop :=
  ∃ (N p : ℕ), N ≥ 1 ∧ p ≥ 1 ∧ ∀ idx ≥ N, q (idx + p) = q idx

def q_seq_step (m : ℕ) (q_prev : ℚ) : ℚ :=
  ((q_prev.num + m * q_prev.den : ℚ) / (q_prev.den + 1 : ℚ))

def q_seq (u : ℚ) (m : ℕ) : ℕ → ℚ
| 0 => u
| n + 1 => q_seq_step m (q_seq u m n)

lemma  odd_iff_not_even (m : ℕ) : Odd m ↔ ¬ Even m := by
  simp [odd_iff_not_even]

lemma  forward_imp (m : ℕ) (hm : 0 < m)
    (h : ∀ (u : ℚ), 0 < u → is_eventually_periodic (q_seq u m)) :
    Odd m := by
  by_contra h₁                     
  have h₂ : Even m := by
    have h₃ : ¬ Even m := by

      simpa [odd_iff_not_even] using h₁
    exact (h₃).elim

  have h₃ : ¬ Even m := by
    simpa [odd_iff_not_even] using h₁
  exact h₃ h₂

lemma  backward_imp (m : ℕ) (hm : 0 < m) (hodd : Odd m) :
    ∀ (u : ℚ), 0 < u → is_eventually_periodic (q_seq u m) := by
  intro u hu

  refine ⟨1, 1, by norm_num, by norm_num, ?_⟩
  intro n hn

  simp at hn
  simp [q_seq, q_seq_step, Nat.succ_eq_add_one, Nat.add_assoc] at *
  all_goals
    try norm_num
    try field_simp
    try ring_nf

theorem omni_math_problem_26 (m : ℕ) (hm : 0 < m) :
  (∀ (u : ℚ), 0 < u → is_eventually_periodic (q_seq u m)) ↔ Odd m := by
  constructor
  · intro h
    exact forward_imp m hm h
  · intro hodd u hu
    exact (backward_imp m hm hodd) u hu

        have h₁₂ := h₁ 2 (by norm_num)

        <;> (try { field_simp [h₁₁, h₁₂] <;> nlinarith })

    have hpos : 0 < x + y := by linarith

    have h_frac_eq : (x : ℝ) - ⌊x⌋₊ = (x : ℝ) - ⌊x⌋₊ := rfl

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  odd_sq_mod_eight (x : ℤ) (hx : Odd x) : x ^ 2 % 8 = 1 := by
  have h₁ : x % 8 = 1 ∨ x % 8 = 3 ∨ x % 8 = 5 ∨ x % 8 = 7 := by
    have h₂ : x % 2 = 1 := by
      cases' hx with k hk
      omega
    have h₃ : x % 8 = 1 ∨ x % 8 = 3 ∨ x % 8 = 5 ∨ x % 8 = 7 := by
      omega
    exact h₃
  rcases h₁ with (h₁ | h₁ | h₁ | h₁) <;>
    (try omega) <;>
    (try
      {
        simp [h₁, pow_two, Int.mul_emod, Int.add_emod] <;>
        norm_num <;>
        omega
      })



lemma sum_odd_squares_mod_eight (a : Fin 6 → ℤ) (h_odd : ∀ i, Odd (a i)) :
    (∑ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2) % 8 = 6 := by
  have h₁ : ∀ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2 % 8 = 1 := by
    intro i
    exact odd_sq_mod_eight (a i) (h_odd i)
  have h₂ : (∑ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2) % 8 = 6 := by
    have h₃ : (∑ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2) % 8 = (∑ i : Fin 6, (a i ^ 2 % 8)) % 8 := by
      simp [Int.emod_eq_emod_iff_emod_sub_eq_zero, Finset.sum_int_mod]
    rw [h₃]
    have h₄ : ∀ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2 % 8 = 1 := h₁
    simp [h₄, Fin.sum_univ_succ] <;> norm_num <;> omega
  exact h₂

lemma not_exists_odd_squares_sum :
    ¬ ∃ a : Fin 6 → ℤ, (∀ i, Odd (a i)) ∧ (∑ i, a i ^ 2) = 1986 := by
  intro h
  rcases h with ⟨a, h_odd, h_sum⟩
  have h_mod : (∑ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2) % 8 = 6 :=
    sum_odd_squares_mod_eight a h_odd
  have h_mod₁ : (∑ i : Fin 6, a i ^ 2) = 1986 := by
    simpa [h_sum] using h_sum
  rw [h_mod₁] at h_mod
  norm_num at h_mod
  <;> omega

theorem omni_math_problem_30 :
  ¬ ∃ a : Fin 6 → ℤ, (∀ i, Odd (a i)) ∧ (∑ i, a i ^ 2) = 1986 := by
  exact not_exists_odd_squares_sum

\[\sqrt{x_1}+\sqrt{x_2}+\cdots+\sqrt{x_n}  \leq C \sqrt{x_1+x_2+\cdots+x_n} \qquad \forall n \in \mathbb N.\] The answer is $C=1+\sqrt{2}$ -/

        (∀ n, ∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, sqrt (x i) ≤ C * sqrt (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, x i))
    }
    (1 + sqrt (2 : ℝ)) := by
  sorry

import Mathlib

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  seq_mod_three (a₀ : ℤ) (h : (3 : ℤ) ∣ a₀) :
    ∀ n : ℕ, a_seq a₀ n % 3 = 0 := by
  intro n
  induction n with
  | zero =>

      have h₀ : a₀ % 3 = 0 := by
        omega
      simpa [a_seq] using h₀
  | succ n ih =>

      have hprev : a_seq a₀ n % 3 = 0 := ih

      simp [a_seq, Int.add_emod, Int.mul_emod, Int.emod_emod, hprev] at *

      split_ifs at *
      <;> try { contradiction }
      <;> try {
        have hsqrt : (Int.sqrt (a_seq a₀ n)) * (Int.sqrt (a_seq a₀ n)) = a_seq a₀ n := by
          simp_all [Int.sqrt_eq_zero] <;> omega
        simp [hsqrt] at * <;> omega
      }
      <;> try { omega }

lemma seq_mod_three_not (a₀ : ℤ) (h : ¬ (3 : ℤ) ∣ a₀) :
    ∀ n : ℕ, a_seq a₀ n % 3 ≠ 0 := by
  intro n
  induction n with
  | zero =>
      have hmod : a₀ % 3 ≠ 0 := by
        intro hzero
        have : (3 : ℤ) ∣ a₀ := by
          omega
        exact h this
      simpa [a_seq] using hmod
  | succ n ih =>
      have hprev : a_seq a₀ n % 3 ≠ 0 := ih

      simp [a_seq, Int.add_emod, Int.mul_emod, Int.emod_emod, hprev] at *

      split_ifs at *
      <;> try { contradiction }
      <;> try {
        have hsqrt : (Int.sqrt (a_seq a₀ n)) * (Int.sqrt (a_seq a₀ n)) = a_seq a₀ n := by
          simp_all [Int.sqrt_eq_zero] <;> omega
        simp [hsqrt] at * <;> omega
      }
      <;> try { omega }

theorem omni_math_problem_51 (a₀ : ℤ) (h_a₀ : a₀ > 1) :
  (∃ A : ℤ, ∀ N : ℕ, ∃ n : ℕ, n ≥ N ∧ a_seq a₀ n = A) ↔ (3 : ℤ) ∣ a₀ := by
  constructor
  · 
    intro h
    by_contra hnot
    rcases h with ⟨A, hA⟩
    have hmod := seq_mod_three_not a₀ hnot 0
    have hAmod : a_seq a₀ 0 = A := by
      have h₁ := hA 0
      rcases h₁ with ⟨n, hn, h_eq⟩
      exact h_eq
    have hAmod0 : A % 3 = 0 := by
      simpa [a_seq] using hmod
    have hAmod0' : A % 3 ≠ 0 := by
      intro hzero
      have : (3 : ℤ) ∣ A := by
        omega
      have : (3 : ℤ) ∣ a₀ := by
        have : a₀ = A := by
          have h₁ := hA 0
          rcases h₁ with ⟨n, hn, h_eq⟩
          have h₂ := hA n
          rcases h₂ with ⟨m, hm, h_eq₂⟩
          simp_all [a_seq] <;> omega
        simpa [this] using this
      exact hnot this
    exact hAmod0' hAmod0
  · 
    intro h
    use 0
    intro N
    use N
    <;> simp_all [a_seq] <;> omega

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  subset_one :
    {x : ℝ | ∃ a b : ℝ, a > 0 ∧ b > 0 ∧ x = (a * b + b ^ 2) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2)} ⊆
      {x : ℝ | 0 < x ∧ x ≤ (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2} := by
  intro x hx
  rcases hx with ⟨a, b, ha, hb, rfl⟩
  have h₁ : 0 < (a * b + b ^ 2 : ℝ) := by
    nlinarith [mul_pos ha hb, pow_pos hb 2]
  have h₂ : 0 < (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2 : ℝ) := by
    nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos ha, sq_pos_of_pos hb]
  have h₃ : 0 < (a * b + b ^ 2 : ℝ) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2 : ℝ) := by
    positivity
  have h₄ : (a * b + b ^ 2 : ℝ) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2 : ℝ) ≤ (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2 := by
    have h₄₁ : 0 < Real.sqrt 2 := Real.sqrt_pos.mpr (by norm_num)
    have h₄₂ : 0 < Real.sqrt 2 * a := by positivity
    have h₄₃ : 0 < Real.sqrt 2 * b := by positivity
    have h₄₄ : 0 < Real.sqrt 2 * a * b := by positivity
    have h₄₅ : 0 < Real.sqrt 2 * (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2 : ℝ) := by positivity
    field_simp [h₂.ne']
    rw [div_le_div_iff (by positivity) (by positivity)]
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (a - (Real.sqrt 2 - 1) * b),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num),
      sq_nonneg (a - b), sq_nonneg (a - (Real.sqrt 2 + 1) * b),
      mul_nonneg ha.le hb.le,
      mul_nonneg (sq_nonneg (a - (Real.sqrt 2 - 1) * b)) ha.le,
      mul_nonneg (sq_nonneg (a - (Real.sqrt 2 - 1) * b)) hb.le]
  exact ⟨h₃, h₄⟩

lemma subset_two :
    {x : ℝ | 0 < x ∧ x ≤ (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2} ⊆
      {x : ℝ | ∃ a b : ℝ, a > 0 ∧ b > 0 ∧ x = (a * b + b ^ 2) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2)} := by
  intro x hx
  have h₁ : 0 < x := hx.1
  have h₂ : x ≤ (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2 := hx.2
  have h₃ : ∃ (a b : ℝ), a > 0 ∧ b > 0 ∧ x = (a * b + b ^ 2) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2) := by

    set b : ℝ := 1 with hb
    have hb_pos : b > 0 := by
      norm_num [hb]

    set a : ℝ := (1 + Real.sqrt (1 - 4 * x * (x - 1))) / (2 * x) with ha
    have ha_pos : a > 0 := by
      have h₇ : 0 < 2 * x := by linarith
      have h₈ : 0 < (1 + Real.sqrt (1 - 4 * x * (x - 1))) / (2 * x) := by
        apply div_pos
        ·
          have h_sqrt : 0 ≤ 1 - 4 * x * (x - 1) := by
            nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num),
              sq_nonneg (x - (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2)]
          have h_sqrt_nonneg : 0 ≤ Real.sqrt (1 - 4 * x * (x - 1)) :=
            Real.sqrt_nonneg _
          nlinarith
        · exact h₇
      exact h₈

    have h_eq : x = (a * b + b ^ 2) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2) := by
      field_simp [ha, hb]   
      nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num),
        Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 1 - 4 * x * (x - 1) by
          nlinarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num),
            sq_nonneg (x - (1 + Real.sqrt 2) / 2)]),
        sq_nonneg (a - (Real.sqrt 2 - 1) * b)]
    exact ⟨a, b, ha_pos, hb_pos, h_eq⟩
  exact h₃

theorem omni_math_problem_52 :
  {x : ℝ | ∃ a b : ℝ, a > 0 ∧ b > 0 ∧ x = (a * b + b ^ 2) / (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2)} =
  {x : ℝ | 0 < x ∧ x ≤ (1 + sqrt (2 : ℝ)) / 2} := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · exact subset_one
  · exact subset_two

        have : p 0 = sInf {y | Nat.Prime y ∧ ¬ (y ∣ 0)} := hp0

            have hprime : Nat.Prime (p 0) := by

              have : sInf {y | Nat.Prime y} = p 0 := by

Consider the sequence $x_0, x_1, x_2, \ldots$ defined by $x_0 = 1$ and \[ x_{n+1} = \frac{x_n p(x_n)}{q(x_n)} \] for $n \geq 0$. Find all $n$ such that $x_n = 1995$. The answer is 142 -/

    ∃ (a : PNat → ℤ),
      (∀ i : PNat, a i ≠ 0) ∧
      (∀ k : PNat,
        ∑ j_nat ∈ Finset.range (Int.toNat n),
          ((j_nat + 1 : ℤ) * a ⟨(j_nat + 1) * k, _⟩) = 0) := by

    rcases hmod with h0 | h1
    · simp [h0]

    intro k

          <;> omega
    have h_nat : (Int.toNat n : ℕ) = Int.toNat n := rfl
    have h_range' := h_range (Int.toNat n)
    simpa [a] using h_range'
  exact ⟨a, hne, hsum⟩

theorem omni_math_problem_62 (n : ℤ) (hn : n > 1) :
  (∃ (a : PNat → ℤ),

  exact h0

    ∀ a ∈ Set.Ioi (0 : ℕ), ∀ b ∈ Set.Ioi (0 : ℕ), a < b → Squarefree (a + b) := by
  intro a ha b hb hab

    exact h0
  have hb_pos : 0 < b := by
    rcases (Set.mem_Ioi).1 hb with h0
    exact h0

  exact squarefree_of_pos a b ha_pos hb_pos hab

  Squarefree (a + b)

import Mathlib

lemma  log_pos_of_gt_one (hx : 1 < x) : Real.log x > 0 := by

lemma eq1 (x y z : ℝ) (hx : 1 < x) (hy : 1 < y) (hz : 1 < z)
    (h1 : x ^ (Real.logb y z) = 2) :
    Real.log z / Real.log y * Real.log x = Real.log 2 := by
  have h₁ : Real.log (x ^ (Real.logb y z)) = Real.log 2 := by
    rw [h1]
  have h₂ : (Real.logb y z) * Real.log x = Real.log 2 := by
    have h₃ : Real.log (x ^ (Real.logb y z)) = (Real.logb y z) * Real.log x := by
      rw [Real.log_rpow (by linarith : 0 < x)]
    rw [h₃] at h₁
    linarith
  have h₃ : Real.logb y z = Real.log z / Real.log y := by
    rw [Real.logb]
    <;> field_simp [Real.log_ne_zero_of_pos_of_ne_one (by linarith : 0 < y) (by linarith : y ≠ 1),
      Real.log_ne_zero_of_pos_of_ne_one (by linarith : 0 < z) (by linarith : z ≠ 1)]
  rw [h₃] at h₂
  linarith

    (h2 : y ^ (Real.logb z x) = 4) :
    Real.log x / Real.log z * Real.log y = 2 * Real.log 2 := by

    rw [h2]

    have h₃ : Real.log (y ^ (Real.logb z x)) = (Real.logb z x) * Real.log y := by
      rw [Real.log_rpow (by linarith : 0 < y)]

    linarith

    rw [Real.logb]
    <;> field_simp [Real.log_ne_zero_of_pos_of_ne_one (by linarith : 0 < z) (by linarith : z ≠ 1),
      Real.log_ne_zero_of_pos_of_ne_one (by linarith : 0 < x) (by linarith : x ≠ 1)]

    Real.log y / Real.log x = Real.sqrt 3 := by
  have h4 : Real.log z / Real.log y * Real.log x = Real.log 2 :=
    eq1 (x := x) (y := y) (z := z) hx hy hz h1
  have h5 : Real.log x / Real.log z * Real.log y = 2 * Real.log 2 :=
    eq2 (x := x) (y := y) (z := z) hx hy hz h2
  have h6 : Real.log y / Real.log x * Real.log z = 3 * Real.log 2 :=
    eq3 (x := x) (y := y) (z := z) hx hy hz h3
  have h7 : 0 < Real.log x := Real.log_pos hx
  have h8 : 0 < Real.log y := Real.log_pos hy
  have h9 : 0 < Real.log z := Real.log_pos hz
  have h10 : 0 < Real.log 2 := Real.log_pos (by norm_num)
  have h11 : 0 < Real.log x * Real.log y := by positivity
  have h12 : 0 < Real.log x * Real.log z := by positivity
  have h13 : 0 < Real.log y * Real.log z := by positivity
  have h14 : (Real.log y / Real.log x) > 0 := by positivity
  have h15 : (Real.log y / Real.log x) ^ 2 = 3 := by
    have h16 := h4
    have h17 := h5
    have h18 := h6
    field_simp [h7.ne', h8.ne', h9.ne', h10.ne'] at h16 h17 h18 ⊢

      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ 2 by norm_num),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ 3 by norm_num),
      Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ 6 by norm_num)]

    have h17 : (Real.log y / Real.log x) > 0 := by positivity
    have h18 : (Real.log y / Real.log x) ^ 2 = 3 := h15
    have h19 : Real.log y / Real.log x = Real.sqrt 3 := by
      nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 3, Real.sq_sqrt (show 0 ≤ 3 by norm_num)]

  exact h16

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  exists_f4 :
    ∃ f : ℤ → Set.Icc 1 4,
      ∀ x y : ℤ,
        |x - y| ∈ ({5, 7, 12} : Set ℤ) → f x ≠ f y := by

  refine ⟨fun n => ((n % 4) + 1 : ℤ), ?_⟩
  intro x y hxy

  have h₁ : ((x % 4) + 1 : ℤ) ∈ (Set.Icc (1 : ℤ) 4) := by
    constructor <;> omega
  have h₂ : ((y % 4) + 1 : ℤ) ∈ (Set.Icc (1 : ℤ) 4) := by
    constructor <;> omega

  simp only [Set.mem_Icc] at h₁ h₂ ⊢

  have h₃ : |x - y| = 5 ∨ |x - y| = 7 ∨ |x - y| = 12 := by
    simp only [Set.mem_insert_iff, Set.mem_singleton_iff] at hxy
    tauto

  rcases h₃ with h₃ | h₃ | h₃
  · 
    have h₄ : x % 4 = 0 ∨ x % 4 = 1 ∨ x % 4 = 2 ∨ x % 4 = 3 := by omega
    have h₅ : y % 4 = 0 ∨ y % 4 = 1 ∨ y % 4 = 2 ∨ y % 4 = 3 := by omega
    rcases h₄ with (h₄ | h₄ | h₄ | h₄) <;>
    rcases h₅ with (h₅ | h₅ | h₅ | h₅) <;>
    simp [h₄, h₅, abs_eq_max_neg, h₃, Int.add_emod, Int.sub_emod] at * <;>
    (try omega) <;>
    (try { contradiction }) <;>
    (try { omega })
  · 
    have h₄ : x % 4 = 0 ∨ x % 4 = 1 ∨ x % 4 = 2 ∨ x % 4 = 3 := by omega
    have h₅ : y % 4 = 0 ∨ y % 4 = 1 ∨ y % 4 = 2 ∨ y % 4 = 3 := by omega
    rcases h₄ with (h₄ | h₄ | h₄ | h₄) <;>
    rcases h₅ with (h₅ | h₅ | h₅ | h₅) <;>
    simp [h₄, h₅, abs_eq_max_neg, h₃, Int.add_emod, Int.sub_emod] at * <;>
    (try omega) <;>
    (try { contradiction }) <;>
    (try { omega })
  · 
    have h₄ : x % 4 = 0 ∨ x % 4 = 1 ∨ x % 4 = 2 ∨ x % 4 = 3 := by omega
    have h₅ : y % 4 = 0 ∨ y % 4 = 1 ∨ y % 4 = 2 ∨ y % 4 = 3 := by omega
    rcases h₄ with (h₄ | h₄ | h₄ | h₄) <;>
    rcases h₅ with (h₅ | h₅ | h₅ | h₅) <;>
    simp [h₄, h₅, abs_eq_max_neg, h₃, Int.add_emod, Int.sub_emod] at * <;>
    (try omega) <;>
    (try { contradiction }) <;>
    (try { omega })

no_smaller_k :
    ∀ k : ℕ,
      k > 0 ∧
        (∃ f : ℤ → Set.Icc 1 k,
            ∀ x y : ℤ,
              |x - y| ∈ ({5, 7, 12} : Set ℤ) → f x ≠ f y) →
      k ≤ 3 → False := by
  intro k hk hle
  rcases hk with ⟨hpos, ⟨f, hf⟩⟩
  have hcases : k = 1 ∨ k = 2 ∨ k = 3 := by omega
  rcases hcases with rfl | rfl | rfl
  · 
    have h₀ := hf 0 5 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₁ := hf 0 7 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₂ := hf 0 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    norm_num [Set.mem_Icc] at h₀ h₁ h₂
    <;>
    (try { omega }) <;>
    (try {
      have h₃ : f 0 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₄ : f 5 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₅ : f 0 = f 5 := by simp [h₃, h₄]
      exact h₀ h₅
    }) <;>
    (try {
      have h₃ : f 0 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₄ : f 7 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₅ : f 0 = f 7 := by simp [h₃, h₄]
      exact h₁ h₅
    }) <;>
    (try {
      have h₃ : f 0 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₄ : f 12 = (1 : ℤ) := by omega
      have h₅ : f 0 = f 12 := by simp [h₃, h₄]
      exact h₂ h₅
    })
  · 
    have h₀ := hf 0 5 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₁ := hf 0 7 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₂ := hf 0 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₃ := hf 5 7 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₄ := hf 5 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₅ := hf 7 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    norm_num [Set.mem_Icc] at h₀ h₁ h₂ h₃ h₄ h₅
    <;>
    (try { omega }) <;>
    (try {
      interval_cases f 0 <;>
      interval_cases f 5 <;>
      interval_cases f 7 <;>
      interval_cases f 12 <;>
      try { simp_all (config := {decide := true}) } <;>
      try { omega }
    })
  · 
    have h₀ := hf 0 5 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₁ := hf 0 7 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₂ := hf 0 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₃ := hf 5 7 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₄ := hf 5 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    have h₅ := hf 7 12 (by norm_num [abs_eq_max_neg])
    norm_num [Set.mem_Icc] at h₀ h₁ h₂ h₃ h₄ h₅
    <;>
    (try { omega }) <;>
    (try {
      interval_cases f 0 <;>
      interval_cases f 5 <;>
      interval_cases f 7 <;>
      interval_cases f 12 <;>
      try { simp_all (config := {decide := true}) } <;>
      try { omega }
    })

theorem omni_math_problem_107 :
    IsLeast {k : ℕ | k > 0 ∧ ∃ f : ℤ → Set.Icc 1 k, ∀ x y : ℤ, |x - y| ∈ ({5, 7, 12} : Set ℤ) → f x ≠ f y} 4 := by
  refine ⟨?ex, ?min⟩
  · 
    exact ⟨by norm_num, exists_f4⟩
  · 
    intro k hk
    have hpos : k > 0 := hk.1
    have hex : ∃ f : ℤ → Set.Icc 1 k,
        ∀ x y : ℤ,
          |x - y| ∈ ({5, 7, 12} : Set ℤ) → f x ≠ f y := hk.2
    by_contra hlt
    have hle : k ≤ 3 := by
      have : k < 4 := Nat.lt_of_not_ge hlt
      exact Nat.le_of_lt_succ this
    have hfalse : False := no_smaller_k k ⟨hpos, hex⟩ hle
    exact hfalse

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  eq_n_sq_of_exists (n a b : ℕ)
    (h₁ : 4 * a + 5 * b = n * n) (h₂ : a = b) :
    9 * a = n * n := by
  have h₃ : 4 * a + 5 * b = n * n := h₁
  have h₄ : a = b := h₂
  rw [h₄] at h₃
  ring_nf at h₃ ⊢
  omega


lemma three_dvd_of_eq (n a : ℕ)
    (h : 9 * a = n * n) (h₁ : 10 < n) (h₂ : n < 20) :
    3 ∣ n := by
  have h₃ : 9 * a = n * n := h
  have h₄ : 3 ∣ n * n := by
    use 3 * a
    linarith
  have h₅ : 3 ∣ n := by
    have h₆ : 3 ∣ n * n := h₄
    have h₇ : 3 ∣ n * n → 3 ∣ n := by
      intro h₈
      have h₉ : 3 ∣ n * n := h₈
      
      have h₁₀ : 3 ∣ n := by
        
        have h₁₁ : 3 ∣ n * n := h₉
        have h₁₂ : 3 ∣ n ∨ 3 ∣ n := by
          apply (Nat.Prime.dvd_mul (by norm_num : Nat.Prime 3)).mp
          exact h₁₁
        cases h₁₂ with
        | inl h₁₃ => exact h₁₃
        | inr h₁₃ => exact h₁₃
      exact h₁₀
    exact h₇ h₆
  exact h₅


lemma n_eq_one_of_three_dvd (n : ℕ)
    (h₁ : 10 < n) (h₂ : n < 20) (h₃ : 3 ∣ n) :
    n = 12 ∨ n = 15 ∨ n = 18 := by
  have h₄ : n ≥ 11 := by linarith
  have h₅ : n ≤ 19 := by linarith
  interval_cases n <;> norm_num at h₃ ⊢ <;> try omega <;> try norm_num

theorem omni_math_problem_111 :
  ∀ (n : ℕ), 10 < n → n < 20 →
    (∃ (a b : ℕ), 4 * a + 5 * b = n * n ∧ a = b) →
  n = 12 ∨ n = 15 ∨ n = 18 := by
  intro n h₁ h₂ h₃
  rcases h₃ with ⟨a, b, h₄, h₅⟩
  have h₆ : 9 * a = n * n := eq_n_sq_of_exists n a b h₄ h₅
  have h₇ : 3 ∣ n := three_dvd_of_eq n a h₆ h₁ h₂
  exact n_eq_one_of_three_dvd n h₁ h₂ h₇

    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - (y + 2)), sq_nonneg (y + 1 / 2), sq_nonneg (x - 3 / 2),

    sq_nonneg (y - x + 2), sq_nonneg (y - x - 2), sq_nonneg (x + y + 1),
    sq_nonneg (x - y - 1), sq_nonneg (x + y - 1)]

lemma  cos_deg_θ_eq_sqrt2_div_two
    (θ : ℝ)
    (h_cos60 : cos_deg 60 = (1 / 2 : ℝ))
    (h_cos45 : cos_deg 45 = 1 / Real.sqrt 2)
    (h_eqn : cos_deg 60 = cos_deg 45 * cos_deg θ) :
    cos_deg θ = Real.sqrt 2 / 2 := by

  have h1 : (1 / 2 : ℝ) = (1 / Real.sqrt 2) * cos_deg θ := by
    calc
      (1 / 2 : ℝ) = cos_deg 60 := by
        symm; exact h_cos60
      _ = cos_deg 45 * cos_deg θ := h_eqn
      _ = (1 / Real.sqrt 2) * cos_deg θ := by
        symm; exact h_cos45

  have h_sqrt2_pos : Real.sqrt 2 > 0 := Real.sqrt_pos.mpr (by norm_num)
  have h_ne : (1 / Real.sqrt 2 : ℝ) ≠ 0 := by
    have : Real.sqrt 2 ≠ 0 := ne_of_gt h_sqrt2_pos
    exact div_ne_zero (by norm_num) this

  apply mul_left_cancel₀ h_ne

  have h2 : (1 / Real.sqrt 2) * (Real.sqrt 2 / 2) = (1 / 2 : ℝ) := by
    field_simp [h_sqrt2_pos.ne']
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> field_simp [h_sqrt2_pos.ne']
    <;> linarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num)]
  simpa [h_cos45] using h2

lemma cos_deg_θ_eq_one_div_sqrt2
    (θ : ℝ)
    (h_cos60 : cos_deg 60 = (1 / 2 : ℝ))
    (h_cos45 : cos_deg 45 = 1 / Real.sqrt 2)
    (h_eqn : cos_deg 60 = cos_deg 45 * cos_deg θ) :
    cos_deg θ = 1 / Real.sqrt 2 := by
  have h_sqrt2_div_two : cos_deg θ = Real.sqrt 2 / 2 :=
    cos_deg_θ_eq_sqrt2_div_two θ h_cos60 h_cos45 h_eqn
  have h_pos : Real.sqrt 2 > 0 := Real.sqrt_pos.mpr (by norm_num)
  calc
    cos_deg θ = Real.sqrt 2 / 2 := h_sqrt2_div_two
    _ = 1 / Real.sqrt 2 := by
      field_simp [h_pos.ne']
      <;> ring_nf
      <;> field_simp [h_pos.ne']
      <;> linarith [Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 2 by norm_num)]

lemma  mem_set_k_plus_4 (k : ℕ) (hk : 2 ≤ k) :

      ∀ x ∈ s,

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  lower_bound_a (a b : ℝ) (ha : a ≥ 0) (hb : b ≥ 0) :
    a / (b ^ 2 + 1) ≥ a - a * b / 2 := by
  have h₁ : 0 ≤ a * b := by positivity
  have h₂ : 0 ≤ b ^ 2 + 1 := by positivity
  have h₃ : 0 < b ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ a * (b - 1) ^ 2 := by
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (b - 1)]
  have h₅ : a / (b ^ 2 + 1) ≥ a - a * b / 2 := by
    have h₅₁ : a / (b ^ 2 + 1) + a * b / 2 ≥ a := by
      have h₅₂ : 0 ≤ a * b := by positivity
      have h₅₃ : 0 < b ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
      field_simp [h₅₃.ne']
      rw [le_div_iff (by positivity)]
      nlinarith [sq_nonneg (b - 1), sq_nonneg (a - 1), mul_nonneg ha hb,
        mul_nonneg ha (sq_nonneg (b - 1))]
    linarith
  exact h₅

lemma lower_bound_b (b c : ℝ) (hb : b ≥ 0) (hc : c ≥ 0) :
    b / (c ^ 2 + 1) ≥ b - b * c / 2 := by
  have h₁ : 0 ≤ b * c := by positivity
  have h₂ : 0 ≤ c ^ 2 + 1 := by positivity
  have h₃ : 0 < c ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ b * (c - 1) ^ 2 := by
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (c - 1)]
  have h₅ : b / (c ^ 2 + 1) ≥ b - b * c / 2 := by
    have h₅₁ : b / (c ^ 2 + 1) + b * c / 2 ≥ b := by
      have h₅₂ : 0 ≤ b * c := by positivity
      have h₅₃ : 0 < c ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
      field_simp [h₅₃.ne']
      rw [le_div_iff (by positivity)]
      nlinarith [sq_nonneg (c - 1), sq_nonneg (b - 1), mul_nonneg hb hc,
        mul_nonneg hb (sq_nonneg (c - 1))]
    linarith
  exact h₅

lemma lower_bound_c (c a : ℝ) (hc : c ≥ 0) (ha : a ≥ 0) :
    c / (a ^ 2 + 1) ≥ c - c * a / 2 := by
  have h₁ : 0 ≤ c * a := by positivity
  have h₂ : 0 ≤ a ^ 2 + 1 := by positivity
  have h₃ : 0 < a ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ c * (a - 1) ^ 2 := by
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (a - 1)]
  have h₅ : c / (a ^ 2 + 1) ≥ c - c * a / 2 := by
    have h₅₁ : c / (a ^ 2 + 1) + c * a / 2 ≥ c := by
      have h₅₂ : 0 ≤ c * a := by positivity
      have h₅₃ : 0 < a ^ 2 + 1 := by nlinarith
      field_simp [h₅₃.ne']
      rw [le_div_iff (by positivity)]
      nlinarith [sq_nonneg (a - 1), sq_nonneg (c - 1), mul_nonneg hc ha,
        mul_nonneg hc (sq_nonneg (a - 1))]
    linarith
  exact h₅

lemma sum_lower_bounds (a b c : ℝ) (ha : a ≥ 0) (hb : b ≥ 0) (hc : c ≥ 0)
    (h_sum : a + b + c = 3) :
    a / (b ^ 2 + 1) + b / (c ^ 2 + 1) + c / (a ^ 2 + 1) ≥
      (a + b + c) - (a * b + b * c + c * a) / 2 := by
  have h₁ : a / (b ^ 2 + 1) ≥ a - a * b / 2 := lower_bound_a a b ha hb
  have h₂ : b / (c ^ 2 + 1) ≥ b - b * c / 2 := lower_bound_b b c hb hc
  have h₃ : c / (a ^ 2 + 1) ≥ c - c * a / 2 := lower_bound_c c a hc ha
  have h₄ : a / (b ^ 2 + 1) + b / (c ^ 2 + 1) + c / (a ^ 2 + 1) ≥
      (a - a * b / 2) + (b - b * c / 2) + (c - c * a / 2) := by
    linarith
  have h₅ : (a - a * b / 2) + (b - b * c / 2) + (c - c * a / 2) =
      (a + b + c) - (a * b + b * c + c * a) / 2 := by
    ring_nf
    <;> field_simp
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> nlinarith
  linarith

lemma ab_bc_ca_le_three (a b c : ℝ) (ha : a ≥ 0) (hb : b ≥ 0) (hc : c ≥ 0)
    (h_sum : a + b + c = 3) :
    a * b + b * c + c * a ≤ 3 := by
  have h₁ : (a + b + c) ^ 2 = 9 := by
    rw [h_sum]
    norm_num
  have h₂ : 0 ≤ a * b := by positivity
  have h₃ : 0 ≤ b * c := by positivity
  have h₄ : 0 ≤ c * a := by positivity
  nlinarith [sq_nonneg (a - b), sq_nonneg (b - c), sq_nonneg (c - a)]

lemma final_inequality (a b c : ℝ) (ha : a ≥ 0) (hb : b ≥ 0) (hc : c ≥ 0)

lemma  hI_ne_one : (Complex.I : ℂ) ≠ 1 := by

  have h₁ := congr_arg Complex.re h
  have h₂ := congr_arg Complex.im h
  simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_two, pow_three] at h₁ h₂ ⊢
  <;> norm_num at h₁ h₂ ⊢ <;>
    (try contradiction) <;>
    (try linarith)

lemma h_sum_eq :
    ∑ k in Finset.range 2010, (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ k =
      (Complex.I ^ 2010 - 1) / (Complex.I - 1) := by
  have h₁ : ∑ k in Finset.range 2010, (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ k =
      ∑ k in Finset.range (2009 + 1), (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ k := by rfl
  rw [h₁]
  rw [geom_sum_eq] <;>
    try norm_num <;>
    try simp_all [Complex.ext_iff, pow_two, pow_three] <;>
    try norm_num <;>
    try ring_nf <;>
    try field_simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_two, pow_three] <;>
    try norm_num <;>
    try linarith

lemma h_pow_2010 : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 2010 = -1 := by
  have h₂ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 2010 = -1 := by
    have h₃ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 2010 = (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ (4 * 502 + 2) := by norm_num
    rw [h₃]
    have h₄ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ (4 * 502 + 2) = (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ (4 * 502) * (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 2 := by
      rw [pow_add]
      <;> ring_nf
      <;> simp [pow_mul]
      <;> norm_num
    rw [h₄]
    have h₅ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ (4 * 502) = 1 := by
      have h₆ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 4 = 1 := by
        norm_num [pow_succ, Complex.ext_iff, Complex.I_mul_I]
        <;>
        simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_succ, Complex.I_mul_I] <;>
        norm_num <;>
        ring_nf <;>
        simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_succ, Complex.I_mul_I] <;>
        norm_num
      calc
        (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ (4 * 502) = ((Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 4) ^ 502 := by
          rw [← pow_mul]
          <;> ring_nf
        _ = 1 ^ 502 := by rw [h₆]
        _ = 1 := by norm_num
    rw [h₅]
    have h₆ : (Complex.I : ℂ) ^ 2 = -1 := by
      norm_num [pow_succ, Complex.ext_iff, Complex.I_mul_I]
      <;>
      simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_succ, Complex.I_mul_I] <;>
      norm_num <;>
      ring_nf <;>
      simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_succ, Complex.I_mul_I] <;>
      norm_num
    rw [h₆]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> simp [Complex.ext_iff, pow_succ, Complex.I_mul_I] <;>
    norm_num
  exact h₂

lemma h_final_eq :
    ∑ k in Finset.range 2010, Complex.I ^ k = 1 + Complex.I := by
  have h₃ := h_sum_eq
  rw [h₃]
  have h₄ := h_pow_2010

    have h₆ : (Complex.I - 1 : ℂ) ≠ 0 := by

    <;> norm_num

      linarith)
    <;>
    (try
      simp_all [Complex.ext_iff, pow_two, pow_three] <;>
      norm_num <;>
      linarith)
  rw [h₅]
  <;>
  simp_all [Complex.ext_iff, pow_two, pow_three]
  <;>
  norm_num
  <;>
  (try
    constructor <;>
    norm_num <;>
    linarith)

    (h_a_seq_def : ∀ n, n ≥ 1 →
      a_seq_val (n + 1) =
        if a_seq_val n < (2 ^ m : ℚ)
        then a_seq_val n ^ 2 + (2 ^ m : ℚ)
        else a_seq_val n / 2) :
    ((m = 2 →
      (∀ n, n ≥ 1 → Rat.isInt (a_seq_val n)) ↔ ∃ k, a₁ = 2 ^ k ∧ k ≥ 1) ∧
      (m ≠ 2 →
        ¬ ∀ n, n ≥ 1 → Rat.isInt (a_seq_val n))) := by

  have h_left :
      (m = 2 →
        (∀ n, n ≥ 1 → Rat.isInt (a_seq_val n)) ↔ ∃ k, a₁ = 2 ^ k ∧ k ≥ 1) := by
    intro hm_eq_two

    have h_main :
        (∀ n, n ≥ 1 → Rat.isInt (a_seq_val n)) ↔ ∃ k, a₁ = 2 ^ k ∧ k ≥ 1 := by

      exact (left_imp m hm_pos a₁ ha1_pos a_seq_val h_a_seq_val_1 h_a_seq_def hm_eq_two).symm

    have h_no_int :

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  tsum_geometric_of_one_div_a (a : ℝ) (ha : a > 1) :
    ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) = a / (a - 1) ^ 2 := by
  have h₁ : ‖(1 / a : ℝ)‖ < 1 := by
    have h₂ : 0 < a := by linarith
    have h₃ : 0 < 1 / a := by positivity
    have h₄ : 1 / a < 1 := by
      rw [div_lt_one (by positivity)]
      nlinarith
    have h₅ : ‖(1 / a : ℝ)‖ = 1 / a := by
      rw [Real.norm_eq_abs]
      rw [abs_of_pos h₃]
    rw [h₅]
    linarith
  have h₂ : ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) = (1 / a) / (1 - 1 / a) ^ 2 := by
    rw [tsum_coe_mul_geometric_of_norm_lt_one] <;>
      try simp_all [h₁] <;>
      try norm_num at * <;>
      try linarith
  have h₃ : (1 / a : ℝ) / (1 - 1 / a) ^ 2 = a / (a - 1) ^ 2 := by
    have h₄ : a ≠ 0 := by linarith
    have h₅ : a - 1 ≠ 0 := by linarith
    field_simp [h₄, h₅] <;> ring_nf <;>
      field_simp [h₄, h₅] <;> ring_nf <;>
      nlinarith
  rw [h₂, h₃]


lemma tsum_factor (a : ℝ) (ha : a > 1) :
    ∑' (i : ℕ), (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = a * ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) := by
  have h₁ : ∑' (i : ℕ), (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = ∑' (i : ℕ), a * ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) := by
    apply tsum_congr
    intro i
    have h₂ : (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = a * ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) := by
      have h₃ : (a : ℝ) ≠ 0 := by linarith
      have h₄ : (a : ℝ) ^ i ≠ 0 := by positivity
      field_simp [h₃, h₄] <;> ring_nf <;>
        field_simp [h₃, h₄] <;> ring_nf
      <;>
      simp_all [pow_succ] <;>
      ring_nf <;>
      field_simp [h₃, h₄] <;>
      ring_nf
    rw [h₂]
  rw [h₁]
  have h₂ : ∑' (i : ℕ), a * ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) = a * ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) := by
    rw [tsum_mul_left]
  rw [h₂]


lemma sum_eq_closed_form (a : ℝ) (ha : a > 1) :
    ∑' (i : ℕ), (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = (a / (1 - a)) ^ 2 := by
  have h₁ : ∑' (i : ℕ), (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = a * ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) := by
    apply tsum_factor (a:=a) ha
  rw [h₁]
  have h₂ : ∑' (i : ℕ), ((i : ℝ) * (1 / a) ^ i) = a / (a - 1) ^ 2 := by
    apply tsum_geometric_of_one_div_a (a:=a) ha
  rw [h₂]
  have h₃ : a * (a / (a - 1) ^ 2) = (a / (1 - a)) ^ 2 := by
    have h₄ : a ≠ 1 := by linarith
    have h₅ : a - 1 ≠ 0 := by linarith
    have h₆ : (1 - a : ℝ) ≠ 0 := by
      intro h
      have h₇ : (a : ℝ) = 1 := by linarith
      linarith
    have h₇ : (a : ℝ) > 0 := by linarith
    field_simp [h₄, h₅, h₆] <;> ring_nf <;>
      field_simp [h₄, h₅, h₆] <;> ring_nf <;>
      nlinarith
  rw [h₃]

theorem omni_math_problem_160 (a : ℝ) (ha : a > 1) : ∑' (i : ℕ), (a * (i : ℝ)) / (a ^ i) = (a / (1 - a)) ^ 2 := by

lemma reverse_imp (m : ℕ) (hm_pos : m > 0) :

lemma  term_nonneg (t : ℝ) (i : ℕ) (hi : i ≥ 1) (ht : t ≥ 0) :

  have h₁ : (i : ℝ) ≥ 1 := by exact_mod_cast hi
  have h₂ : t ≥ 0 := ht

lemma sum_nonneg_expression_eq_zero
    (n : ℕ) (hn : n ≥ 1) (x : ℕ → ℝ)
    (h_nonneg : ∀ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, x i ≥ 0)
    (h_eq1 : (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, (x i) ^ i) = (n : ℝ))
    (h_eq2 : (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * (x i)) = (n : ℝ) * ((n : ℝ) + 1) / 2) :
    (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
        (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1)) = 0 := by

  have h₅ :
      (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
          (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1)) =
        (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (x i) ^ i) -
          (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * x i) +
          (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, ((i : ℝ) - 1)) := by
    calc
      (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
          (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1))
          = ∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
              ((x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1)) := rfl
      _ = (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (x i) ^ i) -
            (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * x i) +
            (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, ((i : ℝ) - 1)) := by
        simp [Finset.sum_sub_distrib, Finset.sum_add_distrib]
  have h₆ : (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (x i) ^ i) = (n : ℝ) := h_eq1
  have h₇ : (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * x i) = (n : ℝ) * ((n : ℝ) + 1) / 2 :=
    h_eq2
  have h₈ : (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, ((i : ℝ) - 1)) = ((n : ℝ) * (n - 1)) / 2 := by
    have h₈₁ :
        ∀ (n : ℕ),
          (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n, ((i : ℝ) - 1)) = ((n : ℝ) * (n - 1)) / 2 := by
      intro n
      induction n with
      | zero =>
        simp
      | succ n ih =>
        cases n with
        | zero =>
          norm_num [Finset.sum_Icc_succ_top]
        | succ n =>
          simp_all [Finset.sum_Icc_succ_top, Nat.cast_add, Nat.cast_one,
            Nat.cast_zero] <;> ring_nf at * <;> try norm_num at * <;>
            try field_simp at * <;> try ring_nf at * <;> try nlinarith
    have h₈₂ := h₈₁ n
    exact h₈₂
  rw [h₅, h₆, h₇, h₈]
  <;> ring_nf at * <;> try norm_num at * <;> try nlinarith

lemma each_term_eq_zero
    (n : ℕ) (hn : n ≥ 1) (x : ℕ → ℝ)
    (h_nonneg : ∀ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, x i ≥ 0)
    (h_sum_zero :
        (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
            (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1)) = 0)
    (i : ℕ) (hi : i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n) :
    (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) = 0 := by
  have h₉ : ∀ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n,
      (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≥ 0 := by
    intro i hi
    have h₁₀ : x i ≥ 0 := h_nonneg i hi
    have h₁₁ : (i : ℕ) ≥ 1 := by
      simp [Finset.mem_Icc] at hi
      exact hi.1
    have h₁₂ : (i : ℝ) ≥ 1 := by exact_mod_cast h₁₁
    have h₁₃ : (x i : ℝ) ≥ 0 := by exact_mod_cast h₁₀
    have h₁₄ :
        (x i : ℝ) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * (x i : ℝ) + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≥ 0 := by
      have h₁₅ := term_nonneg (t := (x i : ℝ)) (i := i)
          (by
            simp [Finset.mem_Icc] at hi
            exact_mod_cast hi.1)
          (by
            simp [Finset.mem_Icc] at hi
            exact_mod_cast h₁₀)
      exact h₁₅
    exact h₁₄
  have h₁₀ : (∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
      (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1)) = 0 := h_sum_zero
  have h₁₁ : (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≥ 0 := h₉ i hi
  have h₁₂ : (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) = 0 := by
    have h₁₃ : ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
        (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) = 0 := h_sum_zero
    have h₁₄ : (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≥ 0 := h₉ i hi
    have h₁₅ : (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤ 0 := by
      have h₁₆ : ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
          (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) = 0 := h_sum_zero
      have h₁₇ : (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤
          ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
            (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) := by
        have h₁₈ :
            (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤
              ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
                (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) := by
          have h₁₉ :
              (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤
                (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) := le_rfl
          have h₂₀ :
              (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤
                ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
                  (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) := by
            have h₂₁ :
                (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) ≤
                  ∑ j in Finset.Icc 1 n,
                    (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) := by
              apply le_trans _ (Finset.single_le_sum (fun j hj => by
                have h₂₂ : (x j) ^ j - (j : ℝ) * x j + ((j : ℝ) - 1) ≥ 0 := h₉ j hj
                linarith) hi)
              <;> simp_all [Finset.mem_Icc]
              <;> nlinarith
            exact h₂₁
          exact h₂₀
        exact h₁₈
      linarith
    linarith
  exact h₁₂

lemma x_i_eq_one
    (n : ℕ) (hn : n ≥ 1) (x : ℕ → ℝ)
    (h_nonneg : ∀ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, x i ≥ 0)
    (h_eq1 : (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, (x i) ^ i) = (n : ℝ))
    (h_eq2 : (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * (x i)) = (n : ℝ) * ((n : ℝ) + 1) / 2)
    (i : ℕ) (hi : i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n) :
    x i = 1 := by
  have h₅ :
      (∑ i in Finset.Icc 1 n,
          (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1)) = 0 :=
    sum_nonneg_expression_eq_zero (n := n) (hn := hn) (x := x)
      (h_nonneg := h_nonneg) (h_eq1 := h_eq1) (h_eq2 := h_eq2)
  have h₆ :
      (x i) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * x i + ((i : ℝ) - 1) = 0 :=
    each_term_eq_zero (n := n) (hn := hn) (x := x) (h_nonneg := h_nonneg)
      (h_sum_zero := h₅) (i := i) (hi := hi)
  have h₇ : x i ≥ 0 := h_nonneg i hi
  have h₈ : (i : ℕ) ≥ 1 := by
    simp [Finset.mem_Icc] at hi
    exact hi.1
  have h₉ : (i : ℝ) ≥ 1 := by exact_mod_cast h₈
  have h₁₀ : (x i : ℝ) ≥ 0 := by exact_mod_cast h₇
  have h₁₁ :
      (x i : ℝ) ^ i - (i : ℝ) * (x i : ℝ) + ((i : ℝ) - 1) = 0 := by
    exact_mod_cast h₆
  have h₁₂ : (x i : ℝ) = 1 := by
    have h₁₃ :

          (i : ℕ) ≥ 1 → t ≥ 0 →
            t ^ i - (i : ℝ) * t + ((i : ℝ) - 1) = 0 → t = 1 := by

        have h₁₉ :

          have h₂₁ : t ≥ 0 := ht
          have h₂₂ : t ≠ 1 := h₁₈
          have h₂₃ :

            have h₂₄ :

              intro t n hn ht hne
              have h₂₅ : n ≥ 1 := hn
              have h₂₆ : t ≥ 0 := ht
              have h₂₇ : t ≠ 1 := hne
              have h₂₈ :
                  t ^ n - (n : ℝ) * t + ((n : ℝ) - 1) > 0 := by
                have h₂₉ :
                    ∀ (t : ℝ) (n : ℕ), n ≥ 1 → t ≥ 0 → t ≠ 1 →
                      t ^ n - (n : ℝ) * t + ((n : ℝ) - 1) > 0 := by
                  intro t n hn ht hne
                  have h₃₀ : n ≥ 1 := hn
                  have h₃₁ : t ≥ 0 := ht
                  have h₃₂ : t ≠ 1 := hne
                  have h₃₃ :

                    have h₃₅ : t ≥ 0 := ht

                    ·

                          t ^ n - (n : ℝ) * t + ((n : ℝ) - 1) > 0 := by

                              t ^ n - (n : ℝ) * t + ((n : ℝ) - 1) > 0 := by

                            (try nlinarith) <;>

                      have h₃₉ :

                        have h₄₀ :

                          intro n hn

                                  nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos (sub_pos.mpr h₃₈), sq_nonneg (t - 1)]
                                }) <;>
                              (try
                                {
                                  cases' le_or_lt 0 (t ^ (n + 1)) with h h <;>

  have h₁₃ : x i = 1 := by

theorem omni_math_problem_170
  (n : ℕ)
  (hn : n ≥ 1)
  (x : ℕ → ℝ)
  (h_nonneg : ∀ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, x i ≥ 0)

  (h_eq2 : (∑ i ∈ Finset.Icc 1 n, (i : ℝ) * (x i)) = (n : ℝ) * ((n : ℝ) + 1) / 2) :

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  mem_162sqrt3 :
    (162 * Real.sqrt 3) ∈
      { t : ℝ |
        ∃ (x y z : ℝ),
          0 < x ∧ 0 < y ∧ 0 < z ∧
          x + y + z = x * y * z ∧
          t = x ^ 7 * (y * z - 1) + y ^ 7 * (z * x - 1) + z ^ 7 * (x * y - 1) } := by

  have hpos : 0 < Real.sqrt 3 := Real.sqrt_pos.mpr (by norm_num)

  have hsum : Real.sqrt 3 + Real.sqrt 3 + Real.sqrt 3 = Real.sqrt 3 * Real.sqrt 3 * Real.sqrt 3 := by
    have hsq : Real.sqrt 3 * Real.sqrt 3 = (3 : ℝ) := by
      have : (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 2 = (3 : ℝ) := by
        simpa [Real.sq_sqrt (by norm_num : (0 : ℝ) ≤ 3)] using rfl
      simpa [pow_two] using this
    nlinarith [hsq]

  have hpow7 : (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) ^ 7 = 27 * Real.sqrt 3 := by
    have hsq : (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 2 = (3 : ℝ) := by
      simpa [Real.sq_sqrt (by norm_num : (0 : ℝ) ≤ 3)] using rfl
    have h6 : (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 6 = (27 : ℝ) := by
      calc
        (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 6 = ((Real.sqrt 3) ^ 2) ^ 3 := by ring
        _ = (3 : ℝ) ^ 3 := by simpa [hsq]
        _ = 27 := by norm_num
    calc
      (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 7 = (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 6 * Real.sqrt 3 := by ring
      _ = 27 * Real.sqrt 3 := by simpa [h6]

  have hval :
      (162 * Real.sqrt 3) =
        (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) ^ 7 * ((Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) * (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) - 1) +
          (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) ^ 7 * ((Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) * (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) - 1) +
          (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) ^ 7 * ((Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) * (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) - 1) := by
    have hmul : (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) * (Real.sqrt 3 : ℝ) = (3 : ℝ) := by
      have : (Real.sqrt 3) ^ 2 = (3 : ℝ) := by
        simpa [Real.sq_sqrt (by norm_num : (0 : ℝ) ≤ 3)] using rfl
      simpa [pow_two] using this
    calc
      (162 * Real.sqrt 3) = 3 * (27 * Real.sqrt 3) * 2 := by ring

lemma  one_case (n : ℕ) (hn_pos : n > 0) (h : n = 1) :
    (∀ k : ℕ, k > 0 → k ∣ n → (k ^ 2 + k + 1) ∣ (n ^ 2 + n + 1)) := by
  subst h
  intro k hk₁ hk₂
  have : k ∣ 1 := by simpa using hk₂
  have hk : k = 1 := Nat.le_antisymm (Nat.le_of_dvd (by norm_num) this) (Nat.succ_le_of_lt hk₁)
  subst hk
  norm_num

lemma prime_case (n : ℕ) (hn_pos : n > 0)
    (h : Nat.Prime n ∧ n % 3 = 1) :
    (∀ k : ℕ, k > 0 → k ∣ n → (k ^ 2 + k + 1) ∣ (n ^ 2 + n + 1)) := by
  rcases h with ⟨hprime, hmod⟩
  intro k hk₁ hk₂
  have h_eq : k = 1 ∨ k = n := by
    have := Nat.Prime.eq_one_or_self_of_dvd hprime k hk₂
    tauto
  rcases h_eq with rfl | rfl
  · 
    have h3 : 3 ∣ n ^ 2 + n + 1 := by
      have h' : (n ^ 2 + n + 1) % 3 = 0 := by
        simp [hmod, pow_two, Nat.add_mod, Nat.mul_mod] <;> norm_num
      exact Nat.dvd_of_mod_eq_zero h'
    
    have : (1 ^ 2 + 1 + 1) = 3 := by norm_num
    simpa [this] using h3
  · 
    exact Nat.dvd_refl _

lemma square_prime_case (n : ℕ) (hn_pos : n > 0)
    (h : ∃ p : ℕ, Nat.Prime p ∧ p ≠ 3 ∧ n = p ^ 2) :
    (∀ k : ℕ, k > 0 → k ∣ n → (k ^ 2 + k + 1) ∣ (n ^ 2 + n + 1)) := by
  rcases h with ⟨p, hp, hp_ne, rfl⟩
  intro k hk₁ hk₂
  have hcases : k = 1 ∨ k = p ∨ k = p ^ 2 := by
    sorry   
  rcases hcases with rfl | rfl | rfl

  · sorry   
  · sorry

    (h : ∀ k : ℕ, k > 0 → k ∣ n → (k ^ 2 + k + 1) ∣ (n ^ 2 + n + 1)) :
    n = 1 ∨ (Nat.Prime n ∧ n % 3 = 1) ∨ (∃ p : ℕ, Nat.Prime p ∧ p ≠ 3 ∧ n = p ^ 2) := by
  by_cases h1 : n = 1

lemma  h1 (a : ℝ) (ha : a ≠ 0) (h : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = 3) :
    a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 = 0 := by
  have h₂ : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = 3 := h
  have h₃ : a ^ 2 + 1 / a ^ 2 = 1 := by
    have h₄ : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = 3 := h₂
    have h₅ : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = a ^ 2 + 2 + 1 / a ^ 2 := by
      have h₆ : a ≠ 0 := ha
      field_simp [h₆]
      <;> ring_nf
      <;> field_simp [h₆]
      <;> ring_nf
    rw [h₅] at h₄
    have h₇ : a ^ 2 + 2 + 1 / a ^ 2 = 3 := by linarith
    have h₈ : a ^ 2 + 1 / a ^ 2 = 1 := by linarith
    exact h₈
  have h₉ : a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 = 0 := by
    have h₁₀ : a ≠ 0 := ha
    have h₁₁ : a ^ 2 + 1 / a ^ 2 = 1 := h₃
    field_simp [h₁₀] at h₁₁ ⊢
    nlinarith [sq_pos_of_ne_zero h₁₀]
  exact h₉


lemma h2 (a : ℝ) (ha : a ≠ 0) (h : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = 3) :
    a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 > 0 := by
  have h3 : a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 = (a ^ 2 - 1) ^ 2 + a ^ 2 := by
    ring_nf
    <;> field_simp [ha]
    <;> ring_nf
    <;> nlinarith
  have h4 : (a ^ 2 - 1) ^ 2 + a ^ 2 > 0 := by
    have h5 : a ^ 2 > 0 := by
      exact sq_pos_of_ne_zero ha
    nlinarith [sq_nonneg (a ^ 2 - 1)]
  have h6 : a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 > 0 := by
    linarith [h3, h4]
  exact h6


lemma contradiction (a : ℝ) (ha : a ≠ 0) (h : (a + 1 / a) ^ 2 = 3) :
    False := by
  have h3 : a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 = 0 := h1 a ha h
  have h4 : a ^ 4 - a ^ 2 + 1 > 0 := h2 a ha h
  linarith

import Mathlib
import Aesop

set_option maxHeartbeats 0

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  mem_27 :
    27 ∈ {n : ℕ |
      ∃ (a b c : ℕ), a > 0 ∧ a < b ∧ b < c ∧ c < n ∧ a + b + c + n = 100} := by
  refine' ⟨22, 25, 26, by decide, by decide, by decide, by decide, _⟩
  <;> norm_num
  <;> decide

lemma lower_bound (n : ℕ)
    (hn :
      n ∈ {n : ℕ |
        ∃ (a b c : ℕ), a > 0 ∧ a < b ∧ b < c ∧ c < n ∧ a + b + c + n = 100}) :
    n ≥ 27 := by
  have h₁ :
      ∃ (a b c : ℕ), a > 0 ∧ a < b ∧ b < c ∧ c < n ∧ a + b + c + n = 100 := by
    simpa using hn
  rcases h₁ with ⟨a, b, c, ha, hab, hbc, hcn, hsum⟩
  by_contra h
  have h₂ : n ≤ 26 := by linarith
  have h₃ : a + b + c + n = 100 := by linarith
  have h₄ : a < b := by linarith
  have h₅ : b < c := by linarith
  have h₆ : c < n := by linarith
  have h₇ : a > 0 := by linarith
  have h₈ : a ≤ n - 3 := by
    by_contra h₈
    have h₉ : a ≥ n - 2 := by omega
    have h₁₀ : b ≥ a + 1 := by omega
    have h₁₁ : c ≥ b + 1 := by omega
    have h₁₂ : a + b + c + n ≥ (n - 2) + (n - 1) + n + n := by omega
    omega
  have h₉ : b ≤ n - 2 := by
    by_contra h₉
    have h₁₀ : b ≥ n - 1 := by omega
    have h₁₁ : c ≥ b + 1 := by omega
    have h₁₂ : a ≥ 1 := by omega
    have h₁₃ : a + b + c + n ≥ 1 + (n - 1) + n + n := by omega
    omega
  have h₁₀ : c ≤ n - 1 := by
    by_contra h₁₀
    have h₁₁ : c ≥ n := by omega
    omega
  have h₁₁ : a + b + c + n ≤ (n - 3) + (n - 2) + (n - 1) + n := by omega
  have h₁₂ : n ≤ 26 := by omega
  interval_cases n <;> norm_num at h₃ ⊢ <;>
    (try omega) <;>
    (try {
      have h₁₃ : a ≤ 23 := by omega
      have h₁₄ : b ≤ 24 := by omega
      have h₁₅ : c ≤ 25 := by omega
      interval_cases c <;> norm_num at h₃ ⊢ <;>
        (try omega) <;>
        (try {
          interval_cases b <;> norm_num at h₃ ⊢ <;>
            (try omega) <;>
            (try {
              interval_cases a <;> norm_num at h₃ ⊢ <;>
                (try omega)
            })
        })
    })
  <;> omega

theorem omni_math_problem_179 : IsLeast {n : ℕ | ∃ (a b c : ℕ), a > 0 ∧ a < b ∧ b < c ∧ c < n ∧ a + b + c + n = 100} 27 := by
  refine ⟨mem_27, ?_⟩
  intro n hn
  exact lower_bound n hn

import Mathlib
import Aesop

open BigOperators Real Nat Topology Rat

lemma  mem_set_85 :
    85 ∈ {x : ℕ | ∃ a b : ℕ, 0 < a ∧ 0 < b ∧ 45 * a + b = 2021 ∧ x = a + b} := by
  refine' ⟨44, 41, by decide, by decide, by norm_num, _⟩
  <;> norm_num


lemma lower_bound_of_set (x : ℕ)
    (hx : x ∈ {x : ℕ | ∃ a b : ℕ, 0 < a ∧ 0 < b ∧ 45 * a + b = 2021 ∧ x = a + b}) :
    85 ≤ x := by
  rcases hx with ⟨a, b, ha, hb, h_eq, hx⟩
  have h_sum : x = a + b := by
    linarith
  have h_main : 45 * a + b = 2021 := by
    linarith
  
  have h_a_le : a ≤ 44 := by
    by_contra h
    have h' : a ≥ 45 := by omega
    have h₁ : 45 * a + b ≥ 45 * a + 1 := by
      have h₂ : b ≥ 1 := by linarith
      nlinarith
    have h₂ : 45 * a + 1 > 2021 := by nlinarith
    linarith
  
  have h_ge : a + b ≥ 85 := by
    have h₁ : a ≤ 44 := h_a_le
    have h₂ : a ≥ 1 := by linarith
    interval_cases a <;> norm_num at h_main ⊢ <;>
      (try omega) <;>
      (try
        {
          have h₃ : b ≤ 2021 := by omega
          interval_cases b <;> norm_num at h_main ⊢ <;> omega
        }) <;> omega
  
  have h_final : 85 ≤ x := by
    rw [h_sum]
    exact h_ge
  exact h_final

theorem omni_math_problem_181 : IsLeast {x : ℕ | ∃ a b : ℕ, 0 < a ∧ 0 < b ∧ 45 * a + b = 2021 ∧ x = a + b} 85 := by
  refine' ⟨mem_set_85, ?_⟩
  intro x hx
  exact lower_bound_of_set x hx

lemma  x_ge_two (x : ℕ) (h : x + 12 = 8 * (x - 2)) : x ≥ 2 := by

  have h₂ : x ≤ 1 := by linarith
  interval_cases x <;> norm_num at h ⊢ <;> omega

lemma aux_eq (x : ℕ) (h : x + 12 = 8 * (x - 2)) (h₁ : x ≥ 2) :
    8 * (x - 2) + 16 = 8 * x := by
  have h₂ : x - 2 + 2 = x := by
    have h₃ : x ≥ 2 := h₁
    omega
  calc
    8 * (x - 2) + 16 = 8 * (x - 2 + 2) := by
      ring_nf
      <;> omega
    _ = 8 * x := by
      rw [h₂]
      <;> ring_nf
      <;> omega

lemma final_eq (x : ℕ) (h : x + 12 = 8 * (x - 2)) (h₁ : x ≥ 2)
    (h₂ : 8 * (x - 2) + 16 = 8 * x) : x + 28 = 8 * x := by
  have h₃ : x + 12 + 16 = 8 * (x - 2) + 16 := by
    have h₄ : x + 12 = 8 * (x - 2) := h
    omega
  have h₄ : x + 12 + 16 = x + 28 := by
    ring_nf
    <;> omega
  have h₅ : 8 * (x - 2) + 16 = 8 * x := h₂
  linarith

lemma x_eq_4 (x : ℕ) (h₃ : x + 28 = 8 * x) : x = 4 := by
  have h₄ : x = 4 := by
    omega
  exact h₄

theorem omni_math_problem_183 (x : ℕ) (h : x + 12 = 8 * (x - 2)) : x = 4 := by
  have h₁ : x ≥ 2 := x_ge_two x h
  have h₂ : 8 * (x - 2) + 16 = 8 * x := aux_eq x h h₁
  have h₃ : x + 28 = 8 * x := final_eq x h h₁ h₂
  have h₄ : x = 4 := x_eq_4 x h₃
  exact h₄

      3 * x + 4 * y + 5 * z = 0)
  ∧
  -- Statement 2 false: N is not always odd
  ¬ (∀ (x y z : Int),
      (x = 1 ∨ x = -1) →
      (y = 1 ∨ y = -1) →
      (z = 1 ∨ z = -1) →
      Odd (3 * x + 4 * y + 5 * z))
  ∧
  -- Statement 3 false: N can equal 4
  ¬ (∀ (x y z : Int),
      (x = 1 ∨ x = -1) →
      (y = 1 ∨ y = -1) →
      (z = 1 ∨ z = -1) →
      3 * x + 4 * y + 5 * z ≠ 4)
  ∧
  -- Statement 4 true: N is always even
  (∀ (x y z : Int),
    (x = 1 ∨ x = -1) →
    (y = 1 ∨ y = -1) →
    (z = 1 ∨ z = -1) →
    Even (3 * x + 4 * y + 5 * z)) := by
  exact ⟨not_exists_eq_zero, not_all_odd, not_all_ne_four, all_even⟩

lemma  mul_by_eight (mE mW : ℕ) (h1 : 2 * mE = 29 * mW) : 16 * mE = 232 * mW := by

theorem omni_math_problem_190
  (M : Fin 3 → Fin 3 → ℝ)
  (x : ℝ)
  (S : ℝ)
  (h_M00 : M 0 0 = 2.3)
  (h_M10 : M 1 0 = 3.6)
  (h_M11 : M 1 1 = 3)
  (h_M12 : M 1 2 = 2.4)

  (h_col_sums : ∀ (j : Fin 3), (M 0 j + M 1 j + M 2 j) = S)

  have hM20 : M 2 0 = 3.1 := M20_eq M x S h_M00 h_M10 h_col_sums hS

lemma  sqrt15_lt_4 : Real.sqrt 15 < (4 : ℝ) := by
  have h₂ : (Real.sqrt 15 : ℝ) < 4 := by
    rw [Real.sqrt_lt (by positivity)]
    · norm_num
    · positivity
  exact h₂

lemma seven_lt_sqrt50 : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := by
  have h₂ : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := by
    have h₃ : (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 := by norm_num
    have h₄ : (0 : ℝ) ≤ 7 := by norm_num
    nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]
  exact h₂


lemma le_seven_of_mem (x : ℤ)
    (hx : x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50) : x ≤ 7 := by
  have h₂ : (x : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := by exact_mod_cast hx.2
  by_contra! h₃
  have h₄ : (x : ℝ) ≥ 8 := by
    have h₅ : x ≥ 8 := by linarith
    exact_mod_cast h₅
  have h₅ : (x : ℝ) > Real.sqrt 50 := by
    have h₆ : Real.sqrt 50 < (x : ℝ) := by
      have h₇ : (Real.sqrt 50 : ℝ) < 8 := by
        nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]
      have h₈ : (x : ℝ) ≥ 8 := by exact_mod_cast (by linarith : x ≥ 8)
      linarith
    linarith
  linarith



lemma four_le_of_mem (x : ℤ)
    (hx : x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50) : (4 : ℤ) ≤ x := by
  have h₂ : (x : ℝ) > Real.sqrt 15 := by exact_mod_cast hx.1
  by_contra! h₃
  have h₄ : (x : ℝ) ≤ 3 := by
    have h₅ : x ≤ 3 := by linarith
    exact_mod_cast h₅
  have h₅ : (x : ℝ) ≤ Real.sqrt 15 := by
    have h₆ : (x : ℝ) ≤ 3 := by exact_mod_cast (by linarith : x ≤ 3)
    have h₇ : Real.sqrt 15 > (3 : ℝ) := by
      have h₈ : (3 : ℝ) ^ 2 < (15 : ℝ) := by norm_num
      have h₉ : Real.sqrt 15 > (3 : ℝ) := by
        apply Real.lt_sqrt_of_sq_lt
        norm_num
      linarith
    nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 15, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 15 by norm_num)]
  linarith


lemma set_eq :
    {x : ℤ | x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50} =
      ({4, 5, 6, 7} : Set ℤ) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · intro x hx
    have h₁ : x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50 := hx
    have h₂ : (4 : ℤ) ≤ x := four_le_of_mem x h₁
    have h₃ : x ≤ 7 := le_seven_of_mem x h₁
    
    have h₄ : x = 4 ∨ x = 5 ∨ x = 6 ∨ x = 7 := by
      omega
    rcases h₄ with (rfl | rfl | rfl | rfl) <;> norm_num [Set.mem_insert, Set.mem_singleton_iff]
  · intro x hx
    simp only [Set.mem_insert_iff, Set.mem_singleton_iff] at hx
    rcases hx with (rfl | rfl | rfl | rfl)
    ·
      constructor
      ·
        have h₂ : (Real.sqrt 15 : ℝ) < (4 : ℝ) := sqrt15_lt_4
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 15, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 15 by norm_num)]
      ·
        have h₂ : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := seven_lt_sqrt50
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]
    ·
      constructor
      ·
        have h₂ : (Real.sqrt 15 : ℝ) < (4 : ℝ) := sqrt15_lt_4
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 15, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 15 by norm_num)]
      ·
        have h₂ : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := seven_lt_sqrt50
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]
    ·
      constructor
      ·
        have h₂ : (Real.sqrt 15 : ℝ) < (4 : ℝ) := sqrt15_lt_4
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 15, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 15 by norm_num)]
      ·
        have h₂ : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := seven_lt_sqrt50
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]
    ·
      constructor
      ·
        have h₂ : (Real.sqrt 15 : ℝ) < (4 : ℝ) := sqrt15_lt_4
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 15, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 15 by norm_num)]
      ·
        have h₂ : (7 : ℝ) < Real.sqrt 50 := seven_lt_sqrt50
        norm_num at h₂ ⊢
        <;> nlinarith [Real.sqrt_nonneg 50, Real.sq_sqrt (show (0 : ℝ) ≤ 50 by norm_num)]


lemma ncard_of_set :
    Set.ncard {x : ℤ | x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50} = 4 := by
  have h₂ : {x : ℤ | x > Real.sqrt 15 ∧ x < Real.sqrt 50} =
      ({4, 5, 6, 7} : Set ℤ) := set_eq
